{"tid":1278260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"祥嫂洪金梅離世　享年73歲","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T13:06:47.000Z","uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5242db881ae6a5eec7f364fefd646c446b0723","tid":1278260,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:47:12.000Z","msg":"祥嫂洪金梅離世，享年73歲<br />\n07月02日(二) 18:58<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190702/photo/bkn-20190702185854399-0702_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190702194416\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190702%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190702185854399-0702_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190702194416&h=870437a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n73歲的祥嫂洪金梅5月時低調入院，近日有傳病情急轉直下，今日傍晚傳出病危消息。東網聯絡上譚炳文女兒譚淑瑩，她表示收到消息，亦正在求證中。東網多次致電鄧兆尊及鄧小艾，兩人接電話，知道記者來電隨即掛線。至於祥嫂細妹洪國華，記者致電給她，她指剛剛從外地回港，甚麼也不知道，亦沒有回應。祥嫂好友親證死訊。<br />\n<br />\n祥嫂近月鮮有露面，5月時傳她低調入院，女兒和兒子亦有到醫院探望。早前東網致電女兒鄧小艾，她只說：「冇嘢講，普通老人病，謝謝！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190702/bkn-20190702185854399-0702_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190702%2Fbkn-20190702185854399-0702_00862_001.html&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=bc5abfcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190702/bkn-20190702185854399-0702_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e1b25507d1464296519e6dcf92362d91333aa9c8","tid":1278260,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T13:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}